-- Austrian Court Confirms Ex-OMV CEO’s Insider Trading Acquittal
-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 2012-01-12T09:09:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/austrian-court-confirms-ex-omv-ceo-s-insider-trading-acquittal.html
Former  OMV AG (OMV)  Chief Executive
Officer Wolfgang Ruttenstorfer had his acquittal of insider
trading confirmed by an appeals court in Vienna today.  Austria’s Higher Regional Court upheld that Ruttenstorfer,
61, didn’t deliberately use inside information to buy shares of
the company a week before a major divestment.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Zoe Schneeweiss at 
 zschneeweiss@bloomberg.net  